Sentencas: Novel flexible conductive ceramic films consisting of Cu1.5Mn1.5O4, Co3O4 and Al2O3 are developed for the cathode current collecting layer (CCCL) in solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) stacks.
Titulo: Flexible Cu1.5Mn1.5O4 combined with Co3O4 and Al2O3 conductive ceramic film as a cathode current collecting layer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: These ceramic films are prepared by a water-based tape-casting method and sintered in situ at the operation temperature of intermediate temperature (IT)-SOFCs.
Titulo: Flexible Cu1.5Mn1.5O4 combined with Co3O4 and Al2O3 conductive ceramic film as a cathode current collecting layer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The effects of addition amounts of Co3O4 and Al2O3 on the electrical conductivity of the CCCL and area specific resistance (ASR) of (La0.75Sr0.25)(0.95)MnO3-delta (LSM) cathode/the CCCL/SUS430 interconnect sandwich are studied.
Titulo: Flexible Cu1.5Mn1.5O4 combined with Co3O4 and Al2O3 conductive ceramic film as a cathode current collecting layer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The results indicate that adding 3 wt.% of Co3O4 as sintering aids in Cu1.5Mn1.5O4 precursor powder can promote its sintering and thus reduce its contact resistance with neighboring components.
Titulo: Flexible Cu1.5Mn1.5O4 combined with Co3O4 and Al2O3 conductive ceramic film as a cathode current collecting layer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Further combining Al2O3 as the binder with Cu1.5Mn1.5O4-3 wt.% Co3O4, though electrical conductivity of obtained materials decreases with the amount of Al2O3 addition increasing, the minimum ASR of 24.4 m Omega cm(2) at 800 degrees C and a stable ASR of around 27 m Omega cm(2) at 750 degrees C are achieved on LSM cathode/Cu1.5Mn1.5O4-3 wt.% Co3O4-10 wt.% Al2O3 CCCL/SUS430 interconnect sandwich.
Titulo: Flexible Cu1.5Mn1.5O4 combined with Co3O4 and Al2O3 conductive ceramic film as a cathode current collecting layer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: The developed flexible CCCL shows pronounced low contact resistance and high stability.
Titulo: Flexible Cu1.5Mn1.5O4 combined with Co3O4 and Al2O3 conductive ceramic film as a cathode current collecting layer for solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Moreover, it can be easily cut and sintered in situ in SOFC stack, which is promising for the practical application in SOFC stacks.
Titulo: Flexible Cu1.5Mn1.5O4 combined with Co3O4 and Al2O3 conductive ceramic film as a cathode current collecting layer for solid oxide fuel cells
